snippet.title: Dark Nights with Poe and Munro - EGX Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
If you weren't able to make it to EGX London this year, here's the EGX teaser trailer for the "Dark Nights with Poe and Munro" FMV videogame - just a quick glimpse of what we've been up to so far.

Contains violent scenes.

Starring Klemens Koehring, Leah Cunard and guest starring Aislinn De'Ath

Website: https://poeandmunro.com
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1098170/Dark_Nights_with_Poe_and_Munro/
